\hypertarget{s-dung-cross-validation--tim-ngung-xac-sut-phu-hp.}{%
\subsubsection{Sử dụng cross validation để tìm ngưỡng xác suất phù
hợp.}\label{s-dung-cross-validation--tim-ngung-xac-sut-phu-hp.}}

\begin{Shaded}
\begin{Highlighting}[]
\KeywordTok{set.seed}\NormalTok{(}\DecValTok{42}\NormalTok{)}
\CommentTok{#ind.all = sample(1:size_train,size = size_train,replace = FALSE)}
\CommentTok{#test_index=ind.all[((4-1)*size_fold+1):size_train]}
\CommentTok{#data_train=checkoutDF[-test_index,]}
\CommentTok{#data_test=checkoutDF[test_index,]}
\NormalTok{nhold=}\DecValTok{4}
\NormalTok{thres=}\KeywordTok{c}\NormalTok{(}\FloatTok{0.1}\NormalTok{,}\FloatTok{0.2}\NormalTok{,}\FloatTok{0.25}\NormalTok{,}\FloatTok{0.3}\NormalTok{,}\DecValTok{1}\OperatorTok{/}\DecValTok{3}\NormalTok{,}\DecValTok{2}\OperatorTok{/}\DecValTok{3}\NormalTok{,}\FloatTok{0.4}\NormalTok{,}\FloatTok{0.41}\NormalTok{,}\FloatTok{0.42}\NormalTok{,}\FloatTok{0.43}\NormalTok{,}\FloatTok{0.45}\NormalTok{,}\FloatTok{0.5}\NormalTok{,}\FloatTok{0.55}\NormalTok{,}\FloatTok{0.56}\NormalTok{,}\FloatTok{0.58}\NormalTok{,}\FloatTok{0.59}\NormalTok{,}\FloatTok{0.6}\NormalTok{,}\FloatTok{0.62}\NormalTok{,}\FloatTok{0.65}\NormalTok{,}\DecValTok{5}\OperatorTok{/}\DecValTok{7}\NormalTok{,}\FloatTok{0.7}\NormalTok{,}\FloatTok{0.8}\NormalTok{,}\FloatTok{0.85}\NormalTok{,}\FloatTok{0.9}\NormalTok{,}\FloatTok{0.95}\NormalTok{)}
\NormalTok{size_df=}\KeywordTok{length}\NormalTok{(checkoutDF[,}\DecValTok{1}\NormalTok{])}
\NormalTok{size_fhold=}\KeywordTok{floor}\NormalTok{(size_df}\OperatorTok{/}\NormalTok{nhold)}
\NormalTok{df_ind=}\KeywordTok{sample}\NormalTok{(}\DecValTok{1}\OperatorTok{:}\NormalTok{size_df,}\DataTypeTok{size =}\NormalTok{ size_df,}\DataTypeTok{replace =} \OtherTok{FALSE}\NormalTok{)}
\NormalTok{Pro.all=}\KeywordTok{numeric}\NormalTok{(}\DataTypeTok{length =}\NormalTok{ size_df)}
\ControlFlowTok{for}\NormalTok{(i }\ControlFlowTok{in} \DecValTok{1}\OperatorTok{:}\NormalTok{nhold)\{}
  \ControlFlowTok{if}\NormalTok{(i}\OperatorTok{<}\NormalTok{nhold)\{}
\NormalTok{    test_ind=df_ind[((i}\DecValTok{-1}\NormalTok{)}\OperatorTok{*}\NormalTok{size_fhold}\OperatorTok{+}\DecValTok{1}\NormalTok{)}\OperatorTok{:}\NormalTok{(i}\OperatorTok{*}\NormalTok{size_fhold)]}
\NormalTok{  \}}
  \ControlFlowTok{else} \ControlFlowTok{if}\NormalTok{(i}\OperatorTok{==}\NormalTok{nhold)\{}
\NormalTok{    test_ind=df_ind[((i}\DecValTok{-1}\NormalTok{)}\OperatorTok{*}\NormalTok{size_fhold}\OperatorTok{+}\DecValTok{1}\NormalTok{)}\OperatorTok{:}\NormalTok{size_df]}
\NormalTok{  \}}
\NormalTok{  data_train <-}\StringTok{ }\NormalTok{checkoutDF[}\OperatorTok{-}\NormalTok{test_ind,]}
\NormalTok{  data_test <-}\StringTok{ }\NormalTok{checkoutDF[test_ind,]}
\NormalTok{  xgb.checkoutDF =}\StringTok{ }\KeywordTok{xgboost}\NormalTok{(}\DataTypeTok{data =} \KeywordTok{as.matrix}\NormalTok{(data_train[,}\OperatorTok{-}\DecValTok{10}\NormalTok{]), }

                         \DataTypeTok{eta =} \DecValTok{1}\NormalTok{, }\DataTypeTok{nthread =} \DecValTok{2}\NormalTok{, }\DataTypeTok{nrounds =} \DecValTok{20}\NormalTok{,}\DataTypeTok{objective =} \StringTok{"binary:logistic"}\NormalTok{)}
\NormalTok{  xgb.pred<-}\KeywordTok{predict}\NormalTok{(xgb.checkoutDF,}\KeywordTok{as.matrix}\NormalTok{(data_test[,}\OperatorTok{-}\DecValTok{10}\NormalTok{]),}\DataTypeTok{type=}\StringTok{"class"}\NormalTok{)}
\NormalTok{  Pro.all[test_ind]=xgb.pred}
  \KeywordTok{print}\NormalTok{(}\KeywordTok{cost}\NormalTok{(}\KeywordTok{table}\NormalTok{(}\KeywordTok{as.numeric}\NormalTok{(xgb.pred}\OperatorTok{>}\FloatTok{0.6}\NormalTok{),}\KeywordTok{as.matrix}\NormalTok{(data_test[,}\DecValTok{10}\NormalTok{]))))}
\NormalTok{\}}
